description: Santé salads and wraps are never boring. We don’t carry iceberg lettuce, stale vegetables or generic salad dressing. You will find fresh greens such as baby spinach, kale and arugula along with unique superfoods such as sweet potatoes, avocados and edamame. Top it off with just-caught salmon, grilled chicken or grass fed steak for a protein packed meal that your taste buds will love and your body will thank you for!We offer cold-brew coffee as well as something quick and easy to satisfy midday cravings: Our fresh fruit smoothies cure thirst and hunger with a delicious, guilt free experience all while extracting the maximum nutrients with each sip!Santé: Legendary service. Your cravings. Your health. Why compromise?
name: Santé Mobile Café
